Description: The resting Holy family and the flight into Egypt; in the foreground the Christ child stands on the lap of the seated Virgin, a monumental figure, and receives a piece of fruit from Joseph; beyond at right, Joseph leads the way with Mary and Christ riding on a donkey Engraving
Bibliographic references: Hollstein / Dutch and Flemish etchings, engravings and woodcuts c.1450-1700 (124) (copy in reverse)
